column1: #   In case of problem, please report to: cds-question@unistra.fr
#Title: TGAS: Subset of GaiaSource comprising those stars in the Hipparcos and Tycho-2 Catalogues for which a full
#5-parameter astrometric solution has been possible in Gaia Data Release
#(TgasSource) ({\bf Download } Tgas Sources as vo tables, fits or csv
#Column  _r (F7.4)   Distance from center (011.8333333333+66.7200000000)[FK5/J2000], at Epoch of catalog (Epoch)  [ucd=pos.angDistance]
#Column  _RAJ2000 (F10.6)  Right ascension (FK5, Equinox=J2000.0) at Epoch=J2000, proper motions taken into account  (computed by VizieR, not part of the original data)   [ucd=pos.eq.ra]
#Column  _DEJ2000 (F10.6)  Declination (FK5, Equinox=J2000.0) at Epoch=J2000, proper motions taken into account  (computed by VizieR, not part of the original data) [ucd=pos.eq.dec]
#Column  HIP   (I6)  ? Hipparcos identifier (\original{hip}) [NULL integer written as an empty string]   [ucd=meta.id.cross]
#Column  RA_ICRS  (F14.10) Right ascension (ICRS) at epoch Epoch (\original{ra}) [ucd=pos.eq.ra;meta.main]
#Column  Plx   (F6.2)   Absolute barycentric stellar parallax of the source at the reference epoch Epoch (\original{parallax})   [ucd=pos.parallax]
#Column  pmRA  (F9.3)   Proper motion in right ascension direction (\original{pmRA}) (G5) [ucd=pos.pm;pos.eq.ra]
#Column  e_pmRA   (F6.3)   Standard error of proper motion in right ascension direction (\original{pmra_error})   [ucd=stat.error;pos.pm;pos.eq.ra]
#Column  pmDE  (F9.3)   Proper motion in declination direction (\original{pmdec}) (G6) [ucd=pos.pm;pos.eq.dec]
#Column  e_pmDE   (F6.3)   Standard error of proper motion in declination direction (\original{pmdec_error})   [ucd=stat.error;pos.pm;pos.eq.dec]
